OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss vows action on energy
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fahead of first day as PM   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liz Truss has promised to deal with    
OL,6, surging energy costs and to cut taxes, 
OL,7, after she won the Tory leadership      
OL,8, contest to become the next PM.         
OL,10,FPart of her plan, set to be announced  
OL,11,Fon Thursday, could allow energy        
OL,12,Fsuppliers to take out government-backed
OL,13,Floans in order to subsidise bills.     
OL,15,FMs Truss will succeed Boris Johnson    
OL,16,Fafter being formally appointed by the  
OL,17,FQueen at Balmoral Castle on Tuesday.   
OL,19,FThe 47-year-old, the UK's third woman  
OL,20,FPM, will then announce her cabinet.    
